做呢樣嘢，排華唔係偶然發生"},{"pid":"bcbaf135ef5497e9df6e8ca94aa54b986cd95133","tid":802663,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:31:57.000Z","msg":"第二家園計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5326b1d0e5c233e575518c8c7eeb1a0f1998f54c","tid":802663,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"歧視法西斯心理不平衡,大馬華人都是中國人,憑什麼自以為高人一等,馬來西亞只是小漁港,現在自是回復它自身的位置,所以自卑,見不得中國人有錢<br />\n<br />\n話說好掛住以上嘅字句,啲五毛轉對白都轉得幾快"},{"pid":"9de44c71268d0ea3d70d9a24ba59773753728163","tid":802663,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"Malaysian First<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b587f906d54935af280709a9e3af8762c4fe41b0","tid":802663,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"大馬夠彊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4abeebc58f9e3865dcced1c2a0abeaeb03fcad","tid":802663,"uid":13257,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"就嚟全世界都醒覺，係得香港訓哂身"},{"pid":"0cc2eff33c937a8c99d978addcef2be216ee447c","tid":802663,"uid":127988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9de44c71268d0ea3d70d9a24ba59773753728163","tid":802663,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"Malaysian First<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"Make Malaysia  great again <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bf7d95bf6ee3329105771706c2f416806075f7","tid":802663,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1368caf62da30654a0c4d8ee4592b4aa4f54cb2d","tid":802663,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c